                                    <emph type="bold">YES-IN SPEC.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Off/On</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Disconnect connector (400) from the ECM. Turn key ON and note if service/check
                                    engine light stays ON. Light ON?
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>&#160;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>&#160;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Go to next step.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Have Caterpillar dealer diagnose the ECM operation.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="1">
                            <entry>
                                <para>2.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Off</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Locate short circuit to gnd in circuit 97AZ between connectors (423) and (400),
                                    then repair.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>&#160;</para>
                            </entry>
